snippet.title: iHeartRadio
snippet.description: iHeartRadio wants to connect you with to the artists that play the songs you love on the radio. See exclusive interviews, live concert performances, fun challenges and more from top musicians in pop, rock, country, rap, R&B, oldies, alternative and EDM. Visit us at www.iheartradio.com.
